SUMMARY:BATTLE OF THE BADGES
DESCRIPTION:? BATTLE OF THE BADGES — JUNE 30\, 2:00PM–8:00PM \nCome donate blood and cast your vote — HPD or HFD\, who will win? The Battle of the Badges blood drive takes place Tuesday\, June 30 from 2:00–8:00pm at the Historic Houston Heights Fire Station (107 W. 12th St) as part of the city-wide competition running June 28–July 5. Every successful donor receives a special edition baseball cap and a FREE $25 Donor Rewards Store gift card! Use sponsor code HHA8 when scheduling. Click below to sign up and help your team win! \n  \nhttps://www.commitforlife.org/donor/schedules/drive_schedule/416139
URL:https://houstonheights.org/event/battle-of-the-badges/
CATEGORIES:Blood Drive
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://houstonheights.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Artboard-1.webp
END:VEVENT
