SUMMARY:July 2026 General Meeting
DESCRIPTION:Mark your calendars! The Houston Heights Association’s Great American Pie Contest is coming to our General Meeting on Monday\, July 13 at 6:30 PM. \nThink your pie recipe is the best in the Heights? Enter one of our four categories: \n\n\nSweet \n\n\nSavory \n\n\nJunior Baker \n\n\nPresentation \n\n\nContestants are required to enter 2 pies for judging\, and a panel of 6 judges will decide who takes home bragging rights as the Heights’ top pie baker of 2026. Prizes will be awarded for 1st\, 2nd\, and 3rd place in each category. There will also be a Best Presentation Award\, selected by People’s Choice\, so be sure to bring your creativity along with your baking skills! \nWhether you’re baking or just cheering on your neighbors\, everyone is invited to join the fun. Bring your appetite and your community spirit—we can’t wait to see you there! \n\nSUBMIT YOUR PIE
URL:https://houstonheights.org/event/july-2026-general-meeting/
LOCATION:Houston Heights City Hall & Fire Station\, 107 W. 12th Street\, Houston\, TX\, 77008\, United States
CATEGORIES:General Meeting
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://houstonheights.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Great-American-Pie-Contest-2026-flyer.webp
END:VEVENT
