SUMMARY:August 2026 General Meeting: HHA Night at the Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the Houston Heights Association General Meeting on Wednesday\, August 11 at 7:30 PM for a special community night out: HHA Night at the Theatre! \nWe are heading to the Alley Theatre for a thrilling performance of The Girl on the Train. Come early to mix\, mingle\, and sip a drink with your neighbors before the show begins. \nTicket Information: To join our neighborhood block\, visit www.alleytheatre.org/the-girl-on-the-train. Be sure to enter the coupon code HHA before choosing your performance date to access our special community arrangement. \nEvent Details: \n\n\nDate: Wednesday\, August 11\, 2026 \n\n\nTime: 7:30 PM \n\n\nVenue: Alley Theatre \n\n\nWebsite: www.alleytheatre.org/the-girl-on-the-train
URL:https://houstonheights.org/event/august-2026-general-meeting/
LOCATION:alley theatre\, 615 Texas Ave\, Houston\, tx\, 77002
CATEGORIES:General Meeting
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://houstonheights.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/August-2026-General-meeting-IKE-Main-v3.webp
END:VEVENT
